{"id":233012035,"title":"再見，禿頭","content":"本人小弟在下我\n從大二開始禿頭，一開始覺得是洗髮精問題，所以不斷的換洗髮精（其實只是逃避現實)，那時因為髮量依然很多，所以沒有很在乎，一直到大四上，我的瀏海已經捨去了一半\nhttps://i.imgur.com/yuu3VHU.jpg\n我才開始驚覺不對，再這樣下去真的會慘\n所以我開始使用各種萌髮洗髮精（市面上都用過)，然後安慰自己沒事，很快就會長出來，結果https://i.imgur.com/y9izPgL.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/uy8EdAA.jpg\n越來越高的髮際線，越來越禿的頭頂，心都涼了\n最後沒辦法只好去看醫生\n然後我就開始吃藥，然後狂用生髮水，真的是狂用那種，去當兵我也狂用，到現在，我也治療了大概兩年了，總算看到了收穫，整個開心\nhttps://i.imgur.com/1JLpYwt.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/f9Iz3xF.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/o3DRzAU.jpg\n最後，我知道我跟禿是一輩子分不開的，但我至少要努力撐到35+，各位禿頭佬，一起加油","excerpt":"本人小弟在下我，從大二開始禿頭，一開始覺得是洗髮精問題，所以不斷的換洗髮精（其實只是逃避現實），那時因為髮量依然很多，所以沒有很在乎，一直到大四上，我的瀏海已經捨去了一半，我才開始驚覺不對，再這樣下去","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"62268850-d2b4-4c21-a7a3-26e71702a276","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-03T22:27:40.415Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T22:27:40.415Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":8,"tags":[],"topics":["髮型","洗髮精","分享"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美髮","forumAlias":"hairsalon","school":"中華醫事科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":8}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/yuu3VHU.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/y9izPgL.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/uy8EdAA.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/1JLpYwt.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/f9Iz3xF.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/o3DRzAU.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"778099c9-2b56-43a8-b0c9-7afb6c15d80a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/yuu3VHUl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/yuu3VHUl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/yuu3VHUl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-03T22:27:40.415Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T22:27:40.415Z"},{"id":"778099c9-2b56-43a8-b0c9-7afb6c15d80a","u